AT PZEV PZEV credits credits 2,000 6,000
Company B intermediate volume manufacturer CA Vehicle ZEV credits Pure AT PZEV Volume required ZEV credits PZEV credits credits 30,000 3,000 Not required Not required 3,000
After regulatory change Combined Company CA Vehicle ZEV credits Volume required 130,000 13,000
Pure ZEV credits 2,600
